 As suddenly as a bolt of lightning would flash, Delilah was so suddenly hit with the force of a flood of news from that of the ancients that it sent her flying across the fire and hitting the tree that was where a spear had hit.<br>
<br>
The music stopped abruptly as the younger amazons rushed over to see what the matter was, but she groaned and told them to leave to their huts at once with a wince. She pulled herself to her feet, her mind with a new thought as she read the scroll that was attached to the tree by the spear. Her eyes closed and she walked away from it, to her hut to prepare in help to Alysia.. the bonfire would extinguish itself within the hour and she would be off to Scynthia to help a fellow amazon.<br>
<br>
