Out from behind the curtains that covered her door..she appeared.  And quickly moved to the center of the village, grabbing the reigns of her mare that had waited outside.  Hippolyte was dressed in full war leathers, her Queen's mask capped on top of her head.  Her brown eyes danced over the faces of those who had taken notice as she took the dais.<br>
<br>
&quot;Amazons!  Our athelfi in Scynthia are begin attacked.  We must quickly ride and unite with them in a strength unmatched by any.  Prepare yourselves and quickly follow me to Scynthia.&quot; Hippolyte then jumped of the dais and onto the back of her mare...pulling the reigns tightly to the side...turning the steed to the side. <br>
<br>
Hippolyte sat on her mare, awaiting those who would follow.  Her gut wanting to rush out of Themiscrya at the moment...but her wisdom...telling her to wait. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazondelerium.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon DeLerium</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon</span><br>  Posts: 82<br> <font color=#993300>(8/17/01 3:24:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=271.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/deleriuml9/images/del2.bmp WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Amazons Unite</span><hr size=1> ~ DeL ran quickly into her hut almost bumping into the Amazon children, one there she quickly dressed and grabbed her wolf warmask, she put it on, and pulled it up so her face would be revealed. She ran from her hut to her mare that was teethered behind it, quickly she untied and mounted it, she quickly rode to the middle of the village to wait with Hippolyte~ <p>~*Amazon DeLerium*~
